{"tid":754283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國航空拒將台灣歸類中國　中國外交部放話：拭目以待","createTime":"2018-07-24T09:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T23:34:33.000Z","uid":35790,"like":127,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"852dd85c40c81eaaefffcfde800020c8742f1e05","tid":754283,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"美航拒將台灣歸類中國　陸外交部放話：拭目以待<br />\n<br />\n建立時間：2018/07/24 16:45<br />\n<br />\n7月25日是中國民航局要求外國航空公司矮化台灣、修改台灣名稱的最後期限，直至今天，美國數家航空公司仍然拒絕屈服中國壓力。對此，中國外交部今天放話，「拭目以待」！<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部今天例行記者會上，有外媒記者詢問中美政府是否就此問題進行溝通？中國外交部發言人耿爽表示，「一個中國原則是國際社會的共識，堅持一個中國原則是中美關係穩定發展的政治基礎。一個中國原則不容談判和磋商。希望美國政府敦促有關企業恪守一個中國原則，儘快做出整改」。<br />\n<br />\n外媒記者再追問「如果美國航企在期限後仍然拒絕做出整改，中方會採取什麼行動？是否會禁止這些航空企業使用中國的機場？」<br />\n<br />\n對此，耿爽說：「讓我們拭目以待。」<br />\n中國民航局對外籍航空公司施壓一事，白宮曾在5月初發表措辭嚴厲聲明，重批中國要求美國航空公司不得將台灣標註為國家，是「歐威爾式胡言亂語」（Orwellian nonsense），美國「強烈反對」中國強迫美國企業使用特定政治語言，呼籲中國停止威脅美國航空業。<br />\n（大陸中心／綜合外電報導） <br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180724/1397584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180724%2F1397584&d=dvfv8g2v7mlOHxVCz%2Bi7up4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=10256799\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180724%2F1397584&h=3b062a79\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180724/1397584</a>"},{"pid":"6a42c52747e0eed98ce227f32e301e786056e343","tid":754283,"uid":37661,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:39:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IwMT-nSfh8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIwMT-nSfh8A&d=dvfv8g2v7mlOHxVCz%2Bi7up4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=c51d0e36\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IwMT-nSfh8A</a>"},{"pid":"fcf178b2659ebd46ed6438b2712f3ce5b7094bba","tid":754283,"uid":35790,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:40:23.000Z","msg":"唔俾美航用中國機場？"},{"pid":"51c0fdf087c44c2c124d9db3990f86ce1482b2ea","tid":754283,"uid":70183,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:40:41.000Z","msg":"我就放長雙眼"},{"pid":"9bdc8bb4fbafe5c8e742510cfe694f006e148e9c","tid":754283,"uid":39628,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"fcf178b2659ebd46ed6438b2712f3ce5b7094bba","tid":754283,"uid":35790,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:40:23.000Z","msg":"唔俾美航用中國機場？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:41:16.000Z","msg":"到時唔批簽証lor<br />\n反正無生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e562ef47392fcee9c545f3cb72d88fc5f779d2b6","tid":754283,"uid":187957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"#爆足一周"},{"pid":"26427d38eeb2e4f1e8685322ace51bdb6d2800d3","tid":754283,"uid":29540,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:44:16.000Z","msg":"拭目以待<br />\n然後<br />\n就沒有然後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03201b40d4f02f23305262806cf922f0593e707c","tid":754283,"uid":187978,"like":117,"dislike":0,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:44:49.000Z","msg":"其實美國人去唔到中國驚啲定中國人去唔到美國驚啲"},{"pid":"ee5ec298842e9aa6fdfe4bb7588cf8ed2e07acb5","tid":754283,"uid":3167,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:44:56.000Z","msg":"中國人唔去美國?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04c096124bd12f4eff16b1ecd73fa33a157677e","tid":754283,"uid":53577,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:45:15.000Z","msg":"等睇侵侵禁止大陸飛機飛美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3809f04162cab0ebcd768ae3df7eceac1053b63","tid":754283,"uid":41205,"like":16